snippet.title: Man-at-Arms Trailer
snippet.description:
The Man-at-Arms is just over the horizon. Watch the trailer to find out when. For more information: www.pvkii.com

Music: 
"Hark the Herald" by Jaldaboath

Horse placeholder model by 3dregenerator (http://tf3dm.com/3d-model/horse-883.html), rigged by Francis Charette, & animated by Vincent "Kordaling" Beaudet

Maps in order of appearance:
te_sandstorm by Ubermann
te_cara by Jahhur, Jimonions, Lhorkan, & Sir Bubbles

Video by Crazytalk
